704964f-a.text:
Hinsdale Street, east side, between Glenmore and Liberty Avenues, showing the old Public School No. 53, which later became an annex of Thomas Jefferson High School.  The new P, S. 63 is on Williams Avenue, one block east of Hinsdale Street.

Board of Education of the City of New York
July 2, 1931
